Attorney Grievance Commission of Maryland, 200 Harry S. Truman Pkwy, Suite 300, Annapolis, MD 21401, Petitioner,
v.
Jing Tan, Esquire Respondent. Misc. Docket AG No. 39
Sept. Term, 2016 Court of Appeals of Maryland. September 22, 2016

ORDER

This matter having come before the Court upon the filing of a Joint Consent Motion for Suspension, it is this 22nd day of September, 2016,

ORDERED, by the Court of Appeals of Maryland, in accordance with Maryland Rule 19-737, that Respondent Jing Tan, Esquire, is hereby suspended from the practice of law in Maryland for sixty (60) days based on her misconduct involving the former Maryland Lawyers' Rules of Professional Conduct (MLRPC) 1.1, 1.4, 1.5, 1.6(a), 1.15(a), 7.1(a) and 8.4(a) and (d).
